      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四小道",
        "王飞天"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王飞天上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "点绛唇",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身入空门，怀抱杀心，好吃荤，不念经文，最好美佳人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走遍天下是某家，哪怕律条共王法。一身霸占蜈蚣岭，观中缺少一枝花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾，王飞天，道号蜈蚣道。在这蜈蚣岭上，三清观内出家，倒也逍遥自在，只\n是少一美女陪伴。岭下有一家富户，他有一女子，生得十分美貌，也曾命人前\n去提亲，无奈他父，再三不允。今当清明佳节，他父女必定上坟插柳，不免将\n徒弟们唤出，想一妙计。\n众徒弟走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小道同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小道",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "出家不会诵经文，随同师父胡乱行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小道",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小道",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将弟子们唤出，有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因张家女子，十分美貌，提亲不允，为师时时挂念，今乃清明佳节，他父女\n必定上坟祭扫。特将你等唤将出来，想一妙计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小道",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难，待弟子们下得岭去，将那女子，抢上山来，与师父成亲，岂不是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此计甚好，你等速速前去，需要小心，不可惊吓那女子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四小道",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小道同下。老道暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老道，你将纱窗打开，准备好酒鸡肉，等候某家成亲便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王飞天下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "四小道→王飞天",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "王飞天→四小道",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "王飞天→老道",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
