    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "武松",
        "王飞天",
        "院子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王飞天上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众徒弟走上！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小道同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王飞天",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王飞天下。武松追上，杀四小道，四小道同下。王飞天上，武松刀砍王飞天冠，起打，杀死王飞天。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我放起火来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（放火彩。张女上。武松拉张女同跑圆场，院子上，跪，张女跪，哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多蒙爷爷救命之恩，请问尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若要问俺的名姓，俺就是景阳冈上，打虎的武松是也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "武松",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等下山去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
